data.description: Custom-Built home on 2.53 acres with luxury features! The pleasure of an impeccably maintained, one owner property with big parking pad, professional landscaping. EARTH CRAFT CERT ENERGY EFFICIENCY. Lake Oliver, VA clinic, Fort Moore, river walk, uptown, all very close   The living room features a big stone fireplace and vaulted ceilings.  Double oven n more in the kitchen.  Extensive storage space and custom cabinetry.  Walk in pantry.  Step out of kitchen bar and breakfast area to an outdoor space that is perfect for all your entertaining.  Featuring high beam coved area with a big patio and stone fireplace. Upstairs bedrooms and big bonus, office and workout area plus walk in storage at end of hall.  Outbuilding with RV/boat carport and 2 bay car care out building or any outdoor hobby you like.  EARTH CRAFT SUPER EFFICIENT BUILD!!!  Flagstone patio and cedar. Upgraded alarm sys. outside video, quality landscaping/sprinkler, new HVAC, features Kohler, new paint...Come and see!!
